programme.title: Nimeni on Trinity - paholaisen oikea kasi
programme.desc: Villia lantta ilman tarkempaa paamaaraa kiertava Trinity paatyy polyiseen pikkukaupunkiin, jossa hanta odottaa todellinen yllatys. Hanen lainsuojaton velipuolensa Bambino on kaupungin sheriffi! Tosin Bambino on ottanut pestin vastaan vain, koska on jalleen lakia paossa ja tarvitsee valehenkilollisyytta piiloutuakseen... Kaupungin mahtavimmalla miehella, majuri Harrimanilla on saalimattomia suunnitelmia valtansa ja maa-alueittensa kasvattamiseksi, mutta laheisessa laaksossa asuva mormoniyhdyskunta on suunnitelmien tiella. Harriman miehineen aikoo vaikka vakipakolla ajaa mormonit alueelta... Mutta yhdyskunnan kanssa ystavystynyt Trinity sotkee mielellaan Harrimanin kuviot.

programme.title: Come to Daddy
programme.desc: Kun Norval saa odottamatta kirjeen vieraantuneelta isaltaan, han matkustaa isan syrjaiselle rantatalolle. Mutta hyvin pian han huomaa omituisen tunnelman, ja kaivatusta jalleentapaamisesta muodostuu helvetillinen painajainen.

programme.title: Kostaja haudan takaa
programme.desc: Jimmylla on pakkomielle saada yhteys kuolleeseen aitiinsa mustan magian kautta ja han on pelottavan lahella onnistua. Mutta kun hanen uusi ystavansa Amir yrittaa saada hanet tekemaan vaikutuksen koulun kuumimpiin tyttoihin yksinkertaisella rituaalilla, jatkat vapauttavat pahan voiman, joka voi herattaa kuolleet ja tehda aidista zombien.

programme.title: A Haunted House
programme.desc: Raavittoman hauska ja torkean naurattava kauhukomedia Paranormal Activityn tyyliin. Rakastunut nuoripari Malcom ja Keisha muuttavat unelmiensa taloon aloittaakseen yhteisen elamansa. Pian talossa alkaa tapahtua mystisia asioita ja selviaa, etteivat he olekaan kahden vaan Keishan on riivannut havyton demoni. Ahdistunut Malcom palkkaa manaajan ja lopulta nykypaivan Ghostbustersitkin ajamaan pois pahan hengen, joka terrorisoi hanen parisuhdettaan… ja ennen kaikkea seksielamaansa.

programme.title: Mohawk
programme.desc: Kurt Neumann (The Fly, Rocketship X-M) directed this bawdy tale of a love that was louder than war drums! With a cast that includes Scott Brady, Rita Gam, and Neville Brand, the story takes place on a remote army post where an artist romances a trio of women, just as a vengeful settler turns the army and the local Iroquois tribe against each other. Film buffs might like to know that the cinematography for this feature is by four-time Oscar nominee Karl Struss, who won an Academy Award in 1929 for his work on Sunrise.

programme.title: Man from Utah
programme.desc: WHIRLING ROPES AND SNARLING GUNS IN THE GALLOPING GRIP OF A GLAMOROUS DRAMA! John Wayne stars as John Weston, a man hired to investigate shady doings at a local rodeo. It seems all the riders who are on the verge of winning end up dead. Along with Wayne, this tale of action on the range also stars the usual Lone Star Picture stock company, including Gabby Hayes and Yakima Canutt!

programme.title: Fighting Caravans
programme.desc: Clint Belmet (Gary Cooper) is a frontier scout with his hands full in this 1931 Paramount Pictures version of Zane Greys novel. Hes helping guide a wagon train across the country, fighting off various attacks on the way, and falling for his lovely Felice (Lily Damita). Belmets grizzled companions think he should leave the woman alone, but it gets lonely out on the trail, and Felices charms are hard to resist. Featuring such notable character actors of the period as Ernest Torrence, Tully Marshall, and Fred Kolher, this vintage Hollywood Western still packs a wallop!

programme.title: Raiders of Old California
programme.desc: The end of the Mexican-American War finds a brazen U.S. Calvary captain and his men taking over a Spanish land grant. Albert C. Gannaway (The Badge of Marshall Brennan) directs an all-star cast including Jim Davis (Jock Ewing of Dallas), Arleen Whelan (Young Mr. Lincoln) and Lee Van Cleef (The Good, The Bad, and the Ugly). Also, look for appearances by legendary country and western stars Marty Robbins and Faron Young.

programme.title: Last of the Clintons
programme.desc: Icon of early talking pictures, Harry Carey (Red River), portrays the rugged Trigger Carson, a noble cowboy who infiltrates an outlaw gang in order to expose their rackets. Ordered to kidnap a young girl, his identity is revealed and he is forced to fight his way out of the gang and back to safety. Already 56 by the time he signed on to do this and a series of Westerns for Berke Productions, the stately Carrey (who netted an Oscar nomination four years later) was widely lauded at the time for adding a great deal of maturity and respectability due to his undeniable presence and strong performances.

programme.title: Feud of the Trail
programme.desc: Feud of the Trail places the dashing Tom Tylerr, a B-Western star (and the original Captain Marvel) in dual roles; as a man seeking justice against a band of outlaws, and the bands vicious gang leader. Capably directed by helmer Robert F. Hill (Flash Gordon, Tarzan the Fearless), and shot at the iconic Lazy A Ranch outside of Los Angeles, the film follows Tom Wade, an honorable man with a face thats nearly identical to nefarious gang leader Jack Granger. Using this to his advantage, Wade exploits his similar looks to impersonate the gangster and infiltrate his band of ruffians.

programme.title: The Range Busters
programme.desc: In the first of the Range Buster series, a mysterious figure is killing the help at the Circle T Ranch. The Range Busters are called in to help, but cant figure out the murderers identity. Is it Torrence, a longtime rival of the Circle T, or is it blind uncle Rolph? Ray Crash Corrigan, John Dusty King, and Alibi Max Terhune head the cast. Director S. Roy Luby (Border Phantom, Black Market Rustlers), also has a fine list of supporting players, including Luana Walters, Leroy Mason, and Kermit Maynard.

programme.title: A Lust to Kill
programme.desc: An imprisoned outlaw escapes and goes on the hunt for his brothers murderers, who just happen to be members of the outlaws own gang. He and his beloved hit the trail, but are pursued by local law enforcement, who have their own plans for justice. Starring Don Megowan, Jim Davis, and Allison Hayes.

programme.title: With Sitting Bull at the Spirit Lake Massacre
programme.desc: A long-thought-lost film finally surfaces after being unseen for over eight decades. Created and copyrighted by Sunset Productions in 1925 but not released until June 15, 1927, this silent epic features the superior Native American actor Chief Yowlachie (performing here under the name Chief Yowlache) as Sitting Bull. Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney are ordered to San Pablo, Mexico, to find out whats behind the trouble an American tungsten mine is having. When they arrive, they discover the mine has been closed, the wells are all poisoned and the town is in the grip of a malaria epidemic. To make matters worse, the lawmen have been followed by four gunslingers determined to give the American troubleshooters all the trouble they can handle - and more. Russell Hayden stars.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, Pat and Stoney tangle with a gang of robbers who have hijacked an Army payroll. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan. Originally aired on NBC.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Quick Hide the Railroad
programme.desc: Kate uses her charms to keep Homer Bedloe from catching the train to Pixley. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Bedloe: Charles Lane. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The President Who Came to Dinner
programme.desc: President of the railroad comes to visit the Shady Rest hotel with the intention to terminate the Cannonballs service. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho are falsely accused of robbing a stagecoach. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951. This episode aired in 1951.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Two bandits impersonate Cisco and Pancho, sending the two to prison for robbery and murder. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951. It was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt. This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Following their activity with the Quantrill Raiders, the Younger Brothers return on the scene to commit a bank robbery in Minnesota. Detectives Matt and Frankie work to put a stop to their plan. Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, George Wallace, Gregory Walcott, Louise Beavers, and Sheb Wooley. Directed by William Witney. Epsiode originally aired in 1954.Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: The notorious John Wesley Hardin kills two people while on a cattle drive to Abilene. Matt and Frankie head out to bring him to justice. Richard Webb stars as John Wesley Hardin. Also starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, Howard Negley, Robert Karnes amd John Eldredge. Directed by William Witney. Episode originally aired April 9, 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, Judge Bean discovers that a young vagabond he jailed for a minor offense may be involved in a major unsolved gold heist.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, a con involving the Haunted Hills draws Judge Roys attention. Letty is among those who undergo hypnosis to recall long past events.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Waiting to hear whether or not gold has been struck in the mine, Annie discovers a beloved stagecoach is being driven by the daughter of the owner, whos threatening to sell the stage so he can pocket the money. When word comes back that there is no gold in the money, Annie becomes suspicious and begins investigating. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Annie Calls Her Shots
programme.desc: After a jailed Dobie escapes from jail, Dobie and Tagg find themselves kidnapped, forcing a desperate Annie to rescue her brother. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook go undercover as managers of a trading post. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A trader ignites a war between the Hurons and the settlers. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben helps three deserters, escaped from an Army stockade. Learning what they had to deal with, Ben promises to share the truth with his friend who is in charge of the fort.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: In Old Cheyenne
programme.desc: Roy Rogers plays a newspaper reporter sent to Cheyenne to investigate a reputed troublemaker. While on the scene, he discovers who the real bad guys are, and sets out to right some wrongs. Also starring Roys usual sidekick George Gabby Hayes, plus Joan Woodbury, and George Rosener. This Republic Pictures western was helmed by director Joseph Kane (The Undersea Kingdom, Dakota) and features two musical numbers: Bonita and Linda Flor.

programme.title: Man from Music Mountain
programme.desc: Gene Autry stops singing long enough to take on some nasty land developers in this oldtime western from Republic Pictures. Of course, it wouldnt be a Gene Autry movie if there werent at least a few songs, and this one comes packed with such numbers as Im Beginning to Care, Love, Burning Love, and the title song. Genes longtime sidekick Smiley Burnette gets to sing a few, too, including She Works Third Tub at the Laundry.

programme.title: Public Cowboy No. 1
programme.desc: Gene Autry and Smiley Burnette are back, and this time theyre dealing with some very modern thinking rustlers. These new criminals have taken up the latest technologies to outsmart the authorities, including shortwave radios and airplanes! Can Gene and Smiley get em? You bet! Songs include The West Aint What It Used To Be, I Got the HeebieJeebie Blues, and The Defective Detective from Brooklyn. Gene also gets romantic when he sings, I Picked up the Trail when I Found You...

programme.title: Yellowneck
programme.desc: Location shooting in the Florida Everglades add to this dramatic tale of five Confederate deserters trying to get to Cuba. First, they must overcome snake bites, unfriendly Seminoles, and their own conflicts with each other. How many of the five will actually make it out alive? Lin McCarthy, Stephen Courtleigh, and Berry Kroeger star in this little known example of 1950s independent filmmaking.

programme.title: Daniel Boone
programme.desc: In 1775, Daniel Boone (George OBrien) leads thirty colonial families to Kentucky where they face the threats of Native American marauders led by rebel Simon Girty (John Carradine). Thats just the beginning, for there are even more dangers and clashes ahead for Boone and his party. With a cast that includes Ralph Forbes, Heather Angel, and lovable child star Dickie Jones, director David Howard takes us through one of the most exciting periods in American history!

programme.title: Riders of Destiny
programme.desc: John Wayne sings! Well, not really. His voice was dubbed here, but as Singin Sandy Saunders hes still able to write the code of justice with a blazing sixgun! Hes a government agent out to help a group of ranchers in their battle with a villain who is tying up local water rights. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Al St. John, Yakima Canutt, and Cecilia Parker, Riders of Destiny was filmed early in Waynes career it was his first for Lone Star but the unmistakable swagger is already in place!

programme.title: In Old Colorado
programme.desc: Hopalong Cassidy and his crew get involved in a war over water rights in this feature from Harry Sherman Productions and Paramount Pictures. The intrigue starts when crafty Joe Weller (Morris Ankrum) turns two ranchers against each other, which leads to dire results. This is the 33rd of 66 Hopalong Cassidy movies, with WIlliam Boyd in the role he made famous. Also, look for regular Hoppy co-stars Russell Hayden as Lucky Jenkins, and Andy Clyde as California Carson.

programme.title: The Legend of the Lone Ranger
programme.desc: The Butch Cavendish gang ambushes a group of Texas Rangers, killing all but one. The surviving ranger is nursed back to health by Native American Tonto, and takes on the identity of a masked vigilante, determined to bring all outlaws to justice. Culled from episodes of the popular TV series, this feature is great fun for fans of the Lone Ranger. Starring Clayton Moore and Jay Silverheels.

programme.title: The Light of Western Stars
programme.desc: Knights of the sage-brush roar across the plains in this western drama from Harry Sherman Productions. Victor Jory ( Papillon, Gone With The Wind), stars as a ranch foreman wrongly arrested for murder. The memorable cast includes Tom Tyler (Stage Coach, Adventures of Captain Marvel), plus Noah Beery Jr (The Rockford Files) and in one of his earliest feature roles, Alan Ladd (The Blue Dahlia, Shane).

programme.title: Broadway to Cheyenne
programme.desc: A gang of big-city thugs trying to set up a protection racket out west meet their match in this B-Western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Rex Bell, billed on the old print ads as The heroic idol of young America! stars as Breezy Kildare, a New York detective who happens to be in Wyoming. When Breezy leads a group of cattleman against the well-armed city boys, the bad guys will wish theyd stayed in New York! The rest of the cast includes such favorites from the period as George Gabby Hayes, Roy DArcy, and Marceline Day. (Day worked opposite everyone from John Wayne to Buster Keaton, but retired from acting shortly after this movie at age 25.) Directed by Harry L. Fraser.

programme.title: Born to Battle
programme.desc: Cyclone Tom Saunders starts a ruckus in a Chinese laundry and has to go before a judge. Unable to pay his fine, he is bailed out by a local cattle rancher and agrees to do 30 days work for him. Its not too long before he becomes enmeshed in a war between rustlers and outlaws.

programme.title: Abilene Town
programme.desc: Ablaze with guns and guts and glory! Randolph Scott headlines as a star studded cast in this yarn about battling homesteaders. Director Edwin L. Marin (Tall in the Saddle) spins this dramatic post-Civil War tale that takes place in the legendary cow town of Abilene, Kansas, coaxing fine performances from the likes of Ann Dvorak, Edgar Buchanan, Thonda Fleming, and Lloyd Bridges. Saddle up and hang on!

programme.title: Brand of the Devil
programme.desc: The Texas Rangers tangle with a band of dangerous rustlers in this two-fisted production from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Starring Dave OBrien, Kermit Maynard, and Guy Wilkerson, with direction by low-budget ace Harry L. Fraser.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: In an episode called Koniakers, G-Men Pat Gallagher and Stoney Crockett investigate how U.S. currency in a bank vault was replaced by counterfeit money. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West. In this episode, Pat and Stoney get reports that a man is selling salted mines to investors. The two G-men are determined to discover the truth. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Is There a Doctor in the Roundhouse
programme.desc: Railroad CEO Norman Curtis breaks the Cannonballs throttle lever, threatening the success of the Shady Rest Hotels annual jamboree. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Norman Curtis: Roy Roberts. Directed by David Alexander.Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Courtship of Floyd Smoot
programme.desc: Kates intentions are mistaken when she tries to help Floyd Smoot regain his confidence after being slighted by the woman he loves, a bride he had ordered by mail! Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Floyd Smoot: Rafe Davis.Directed by Sherman Marks. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho must prove their innocence when they are accused of killing the assistant to the sheriff in Bonanza.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 .This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco tries to help a beautiful woman prove that her brother is innocent after hes arrested for murder.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Matt and Frankie arrivein the California gold fields where Frankie is kidnapped by the infamous bandit Joaquin Murietta. Without his usualy partner, Matt enlists the help of Captain Harry Love. Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, and Robert Anderson. Look for Rick Jason as Murietta. Jason would later go on to star in the popular ABC war series Combat!

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Following the murder of a railroad agent, Matt and Frankie work to bring the vengeful Tiburcio Vasquez to justice. Starring Jim Davis, mary Castle,Anthony Caruso, Edward Colmas, Lillian Molieri, and Eddie Parker. Also, look for Glenn Strange as Sheriff Billy Rowland. Strange was known for playing Frankensteins monster in several Universal pictures, as well as a recurring role on Gunsmoke. Also, Eddie Parker, who plays a trapper in this episode, was one of Hollywoods most revered stuntmen. Directed by William Witney. Epsiode oringinally aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.sub-title: S01 : E17 Judge Declares a Holiday
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, the judge meets up with a con man who comes to towns, arranges horse races then skips town with the receipts and all the money that was bet. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, an outlaw gang plans to take over the town by getting Judge Bean to resign over false charges of misconduct. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Valley of the Shadows
programme.desc: Annie tries to help a blind girl find her fathers killer. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. Directed by Robert G. Walker. Also starring Judy Nugent, Forrest Taylor, and Denver Pyle. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Annie and the Lily Maid
programme.desc: Choctaw looks to inherit the ranch of the murdered Sam Forbes, but Elaine, a previously unknown niece, appears, making Annie suspicious as the men fall for her seemingly delicate nature. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: After a long winter, the Tuscarora tribe struggles for survival. Hawkeye and Chingachcook set out to help.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingacchook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Tribesmen war over the daughter of a Mingo Chief. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben and Adam are in jail, about to be hung for a crime they didnt commit. Joe and Hoss must find out why the witnesses to the alleged crime have lied about what happened before the execution takes place. They receive help from a vagrant named Lassiter who is looking for the men who committed a lynching in Kansas years ago.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Down Texas Way
programme.desc: The sixth film in Monograms Rough Rider series once again follows Buck Roberts (Buck Jones), Tom McCoy (Tim McCall), and Sandy Hopkins (Raymond Hatton) as undercover US Marshals posing as outlaws in order to confound their enemies. When Sandy is framed for murder by a gang of frontier racketeers who hope to take over a small town as their headquarters, Buck and Tom must work separately to save their buddy from a lynch mob and foil the crooks dastardly schemes.

programme.title: Robin Hood of the Pecos
programme.desc: Roy Rogers finds himself elected sheriff in a wild Texas town after the Civil War. But can Roy handle a place under martial law? And can he save Gabby Hayes from being executed? And how many songs will he get to sing? Clear the burrs from your saddle and get ready for a good one, also starring Marjorie Reynolds, plus Sally Payne as Belle Starr, Queen of the Oklahoma Outlaws!

programme.title: Song of Arizona
programme.desc: This Roy Rogers adventure finds Gabby Whitaker (Gabby Hayes) running a ranch for wayward boys. One of the boys uses stolen money to help Gabby pay off his debts, but things unravel when the boys father, a notorious outlaw named King Blaine, is murdered; the rest of the Blaine gang show up at Gabbys looking for the loot! Director Frank McDonald works with a fine cast, including Dale Evans, Lyle Talbot, and of course, Roys beloved horse Trigger.

programme.title: Custers Last Stand
programme.desc: The survivor of an Indian attack acquires a rare medicine arrow, and a menacing character named Blade (Reed Howes) will stop at nothing to take it from him. Elmer Clifton (Assassin of Youth, Seven Doors to Death) directs a memorable cast that includes Rex Lease (The Sign of the Wolf, The Monster Walks), Lona Andre (Slaves in Bondage, Death in the Air), and William Farnum (Samson and Delilah). Meanwhile, Frank McGlynn Jr is in the title role of General George A. Custer.

programme.title: Six Gun Trail
programme.desc: Legendary cowboy star Tim McCoy stars as Captain William Carson, who along with his sidekick Magpie does battle with jewel thieves. Its an actionfilled drama of the West, with plenty of blazing guns and heman adventure! There are a couple of songs, too, including Moon Over the Plains but they arent sung by Tim McCoy. He was too darned tough to sing! Also starring Nora Lane, Ben Corbet; directed by Sam Newfield.

programme.title: Blue Steel
programme.desc: Undercover US Marshal John Carruthers (John Wayne) is investigating a rash of robberies by a character known as The Polka Dot Bandit in this B-movie gem. Along the way, Carruthers finds himself in more trouble than hed ever expected! Written and directed by Robert N. Bradbury, the film features George Gabby Hayes, Eleanor Hunt, and many other favorites of the era. Wayne was only 27 at the time of Blue Steel, but was well on his way to becoming The Duke.

programme.title: Outpost In Morocco
programme.desc: George Raft, Mary Windsor, and Akim Tamiroff star in this romantic drama from director Robert Florey (The Florentine Dagger, Daughter of Shanghai). Raft plays Capt. Gerard, a member of the Foreign Legion known for his romantic entanglements. Hes assigned to escort an emirs daughter to her fathers mountain citadel and learn about the emirs activities. Not surprisingly, Gerard finds trouble brewing! With footage shot in Morocco, this movie also features a beautiful musical score by twotime Oscar nominee Michel Michelet (Voice in the Wind).

programme.title: Heartbeat
programme.desc: A puppy needs open-heart surgery, and Chris treats a bunny with heatstroke.

programme.title: Devil Babies
programme.desc: Chris rushes to aid mysteriously ill baby reptiles and a poisoned schnauzer.

programme.title: Cute Compact
programme.desc: Appraise energetic breeds, like shih tzus, that can tire out a pack of kids.

programme.title: Best Show
programme.desc: Connect with three sweet rescues who aim to charm their way into a busy family.

programme.title: Episode 20
programme.sub-title: S02 : E20 Vet On The Hill
programme.desc: Hear devastating news about a lovable puppy and examine a cat’s odd growth.

programme.title: Extraordinary Measures
programme.sub-title: S03 : E15 Vet On The Hill

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsikringsmann som kjemper med tap og kjærlighet, oppdager nye muligheter i en uke full av uventede hendelser og komiske vendepunkter.

programme.title: Another Christmas Coincidence
programme.desc: Toisilleen tuntemattomat Alice ja Jack, joilla on taysin erilainen tausta, paatyvat sattumalta samoihin viikonloppuhaihin. He pitavat heti toisistaan, mutta Alice arkailee uutta suhdetta, koska entinen kaukosuhde paattyi ikavasti. Alice alkaa kuitenkin Olga-aidin rohkaisemana tottua vahitellen ajatukseen deittailun aloittamisesta. Uudet yhteensattumat lahentavat nuoria toisiinsa, samalla kun tielle osuu yha uusia esteita, jotka vaikeuttavat juuri alkanutta romanssia.

programme.title: Mina armahdan Mooses ei (The Troublemakers)
programme.desc: Travis (Terence Hill) on lannen nopein vetaja. Hanen veljensa Moses (Bud Spencer) on vakeva kuin karhu, mutta monin verroin pahansisuisempi ja seudun kovin palkkionmetsastaja. Kun heidan vanha aitimuorinsa paattaa saattaa veljekset yhteen jouluna, saa Travis tehtavakseen houkutella Moseksen kotiin.

programme.title: Tonttutytto Pelastaa Joulun
programme.desc: Kun New Yorkin mafia sieppaa joulupukin juuri ennen joulua- Tonttutytto, aivan tavallinen tonttu, tulee apuun. Han lyottaytyy yhteen ystavansa Saihkyn kanssa- pysayttaakseen pahikset, loytaakseen joulupukin ja pelastaakseen joulun.

programme.title: Joulun alla
programme.desc: CHRISTMAS UNDER WRAPS, esittelee Candace Cameron Buren tohtori Lauren Brunellin roolissa, joka hyvaksyy tyopaikan Alaskassa menetettyaan seka poikaystavansa etta arvostetun leikkausapurahansa, mutta saa tietaa, etta kyseessa on pieni sairaala pikkukaupungissa.

programme.title: Bennettin Laulujuhla
programme.desc: Bennettin ja Songin perhe palaa jouluksi uutisten kera. Rouva Song odottaa lasta 14 adoptiolapsen joukkoon. Perheen on lyottaydyttava yhteen haastaakseen kiinteistokehittajan, joka haluaa sulkea setansa monitoimitalon vammaisille ja vaarassa oleville lapsille. Rakkaudella, tiimityolla ja joulun taikuudella paiva pelastuu!

programme.title: A Christmas in Royal Fashion
programme.desc: Kansainvalisen PR-yrityksen kaunis ja lahjakas assistentti Kristin Cooper saa vastuulleen vaatealalla tyoskentelevan liikemies Carsonin vuotuisen joulun muotinaytoksen ja huutokaupan jarjestamisen.

programme.title: Furry Little Christmas
programme.desc: Suurkaupungin elainlaakari kaatuu pikkukaupungin laakariin, kun tama paattaa jarjestaa New Yorkin joulun hanen kotikaupungissaan Vermontissa.

programme.title: A Christmas Movie Christmas
programme.desc: Sisarukset Eve ja Lacey toivovat joulua, joka olisi kuin suoraan elokuvamaailmasta. Aivan yllattaen he huomaavatkin olevansa keskella jouluelokuvaa. He heraavat satumaisessa ja taydellisessa ”Joulukaupungissa”, jossa on taydellinen joulu ja jossa kaikki on vain aivan taydellista. Mita enemman sisarukset tutkivat kaikkea jouluun liittyvaa, sita enemman he tajuavat, etta taydellisyys ei ehka olekaan perinteisen joulun oikea tarkoitus. Ehka onkin olemassa toisenlainen taika, johon kuuluvat palaneet piparkakut ja kuivunut joulukinkku…?

programme.title: So This Is Christmas
programme.desc: Ashley Young on joutunut ojaan elamaansa ja hengailua vaara ihmisia yrittaa paeta kaikkea draama. Yhtakkia kaikki tuntuu muuttaa suuntaa, kun he palkkasivat kasityolainen kannustaa hanta sietaa 1. Heinakuuta pelata oikeudettoman nuorille. Ashley nakee mahdollisuuden parantua oman levoton perheen kannustamalla muita enemman avun tarpeessa. Yhdessa he loytavat hammastyttavaa, mita voi helposti åstakomma kautta ihana lahja, joka vain antaakseni muille.

programme.title: Joulukuponki
programme.desc: Entinen luistelumestari alkaa opettaa ystavansa lammella- ja jakaa "kuponkeja" houkutellakseen uusia oppilaita. Kun hanen entinen lukiorakkaansa (ja nyt kuuluisa jaakiekkoilija)- tuo veljentyttarensa tunneille, vanhat liekit syttyvat uudelleen- ja joulu on taynna uutta mahdollisuutta rakkauteen.

programme.title: Joulu Kruunun Kera
programme.desc: Kun menestyva nainen palaa kotikaupunkiinsa - elvyttamaan perheensa joulufestivaalin, - han tapaa komean muukalaisen, joka auttaa tapahtuman jarjestamisessa. Heidan valillaan kipinoi, mutta han ei tieda - etta prinssi on valeasussa ja etsii joulun henkea. Vaaditaan kuninkaallinen joulun ihme, jotta heidan sydamensa yhtyvat.

programme.title: 12 Joulukoiraa
programme.desc: Tyoton leski-isa lahettaa tyttarensa tatinsa luo kaupunkiin- joka on kieltanyt koirat. Matkalla kouluun han loytaa koiranpennun ja paattaa pitaa sen - vaikka rankkuri on hanen kannoillaan. Hanen pitaa selvittaa, mita koirille tapahtuu- ja hurmata pormestari ikimuistoisimmalla joulunaytelmalla.

programme.title: Huijarijoulu
programme.desc: Sarkynyt nuori nainen palaa kotiin jouluksi - ja tuntee perheen paineet sinkkuna olemisesta. Rakastava ja utelias sisko laatii suunnitelman - jarjestaa hanelle nettitreffit komean ammattiurheilijan kanssa. Mutta asiat saavat odottamattoman kaanteen, kun mies ei olekaan "saihkyva haarniskainen prinssi", ja hanen lapsuudenystavansa nayttaa hanelle, etta tosirakkaus voi olla lahempana kotia.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Maailman kuuluisimman joululaulun syntytarina. Dokumenttielokuva kertoo, miten nuori Joseph Mohr paatyi kirjoittamaan vuonna 1818 ensiesityksensa saaneen laulun "Jouluyo, juhlayo".

programme.title: Deck the Halls
programme.desc: Menestysmysteerikirjailija Mary Higgins Clarkin romaaniin perustuva elokuva nahdaan jouluna salapoliisitarinana. Naisetsiva lyottaytyy yksiin amatoorietsivan kanssa loytaakseen kadonneen isansa.

programme.title: Joulukuppikakkuja
programme.desc: Kun perheen leipomo joutuu ehka sulkemaan ovensa ennen joulua - siskokset Kimin ja Ginan on lyottaydyttava yhteen - kansallisessa leivontakilpailussa voittaakseen paapalkinnon. Kilpailijoiden ja tikittavan kellon maailmassa - tarvitaan joulun ihme leipomon pelastamiseksi. He saattavat loytaa paljon suuremman palkinnon kuin toivoivat.

programme.title: Jouluhaat
programme.desc: Haley Foster pakeni lapsuutensa pikkukaupungista Pineridgesta ja siirtyi suurkaupunkilaiselamaan losangelesilaisena haajarjestelijana rva Reynoldsin omistamassa eliittiluokan yrityksessa.

programme.title: Hemmetin Joulu
programme.desc: Telepaattisia kykyja omaava koira pakenee valtion sulkutilasta- ja juoksee suoraan kahden nuoren veljen rakastavaan syliin. Washingtonin johto ei luovu salaisesta aseestaan helpolla.

programme.title: A Taste Of Christmas
programme.desc: Kun pikkukaupungin yrittelias leipuri Emily saa omatekoisen joulukalenterin salaiselta ihailijalta, paikalliset haluavat kiihkeasti selvittaa lahettajan henkilollisyyden. Kaupungissa juoruillaan seka joulukalenterista etta Emilyn rakkausseikkailuista, koska kaikki poikamiehet ovat kiinnostuneita hanesta. Mutta Emilya kiinnostaa hanen pahin kilpailijansa, ranskalaisleipuri Gerard.

programme.title: Nothing Like the Holidays
programme.desc: Tassa lamminhenkisessa joulukomediassa Rodriguezin perheen kauempana asuvat jasenet kokoontuvat vanhempiensa kotiin kenties viimeista kertaa viettamaan joulua yhdessa.

programme.title: Bennettin Laulujuhla
programme.desc: Bennettin ja Songin perhe palaa jouluksi uutisten kera. Rouva Song odottaa lasta 14 adoptiolapsen joukkoon. Perheen on lyottaydyttava yhteen haastaakseen kiinteistokehittajan, joka haluaa sulkea setansa monitoimitalon vammaisille ja vaarassa oleville lapsille. Rakkaudella, tiimityolla ja joulun taikuudella paiva pelastuu!

programme.title: Tonttutytto Pelastaa Joulun
programme.desc: Kun New Yorkin mafia sieppaa joulupukin juuri ennen joulua- Tonttutytto, aivan tavallinen tonttu, tulee apuun. Han lyottaytyy yhteen ystavansa Saihkyn kanssa- pysayttaakseen pahikset, loytaakseen joulupukin ja pelastaakseen joulun.

programme.title: Joulukievari
programme.desc: Kun liikenainen Jennifer kuulee vanhempiensa lahtevan matkoille jouluksi ilman hanta, han paattaa jattaa San Franciscon humun taakseen ja lahtea Alaskaan tutustumaan isoaidiltaan perinnoksi saamaansa kievarrin, joka on tarkoitus kunnostaa ja myyda.

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Hienon gaalan jalkeen prinsessa Carly paattaa pitaa sapattivuoden ja aloittaa unelmatyon hiihtokeskuksessa. Yksikaan uusista tyotovereista ei tieda, kuka han oikeasti on. Mutta kun kuninkaallisen suvun jasenia ilmestyy hiihtokeskukseen, salaisuutta on pian hyvin vaikea sailyttaa paljastumatta. Samalla valmistellaan keskuksen 50-vuotisjuhlia ja Carly huomaa ihastuneensa omistajan veljeen Jesseen. Carlyn taytyy tehda suuria paatoksia elamassaan ja han tuntee olevansa yha enemman ymmallaan.

programme.title: 12 Pups of Christmas
programme.desc: Erinin miessuhteen paatyttya han aloittelee elamaansa uudessa tyossa ja uudessa kaupungissa. Mutta juuri kun han luulee paasseensa tasapainoon, han tormaa itsekeskeiseen pomoonsa Martiniin. Mies yrittaa pitaa firmaansa pystyssa ja pyytaa Erinilta apua. Hanen pitaisi juuri ennen joulua huolehtia 12 koiranpennusta, jotka ovat jaaneet toimistolle kuvaustoiden loputtua. Kun Erin ja Martin tekevat tyota yhdessa, tunteet lampenevat, ja rakkaus tulee mukaan sopivasti juuri jouluksi.

programme.title: Joulu Kruunun Kera
programme.desc: Kun menestyva nainen palaa kotikaupunkiinsa - elvyttamaan perheensa joulufestivaalin, - han tapaa komean muukalaisen, joka auttaa tapahtuman jarjestamisessa. Kilpailijoiden ja tikittavan kellon maailmassa - tarvitaan joulun ihme leipomon pelastamiseksi. He saattavat loytaa paljon suuremman palkinnon kuin toivoivat.

programme.title: Avain Jouluun
programme.desc: Kun tyytymaton tonttu nakee tilaisuuden vallata pohjoisnavan- han kaantaa taikakoneella aikaa taaksepain Joulupukista- joka alkaa nuortua nopeasti. Joulumuori on vangittu ja karkkitankovankilassa. Uskollisen tontun, pikkutyton, jolla on taika-avain - ja teini-ikaisen joulupukin on kaannettava aikaa eteenpain - ja pelastettava joulun tulevaisuus.

programme.title: Pahkinansarkija-makeinen
programme.desc: Oli jouluaatto. Silberhausin lapset odottivat innolla juhlallisuuksien alkua. Marie ja Fritz leikkivat lastenhuoneessa, kun heidan kummisetansa Drosselmayer saapuu - ja antaa heille joululahjaksi Pahkinansarkijan. Marie nakee suuren taistelun- Pahkinansarkijan johtaman lelusotilaiden armeijan- ja Hiirikuninkaan komentaman kamalan hiiripataljoonan valilla.

programme.title: Hotet
programme.desc: Lasse Brudell on vastaava ohjelmoija Vidselin lentotukikohdassa Norrbottenissa. Han tyoskentelee huippusalaisen JAS Gripeniin liittyvan EWS-puolustusjarjestelman parissa. Majuri Haglund, karaistunut sotaveteraani, johtaa armeijan erikoisjoukkoja. Miesten tiet kohtaavat, kun Haglund kutsutaan nostamaan turvatoimien tasoa Gripenin ulkomaisille ostajaehdokkaille valmisteltavaa esittelya varten.

programme.title: Jarnganget
programme.desc: Nelja ystavaa ovat jokavuotisella melontareissullaan Kalix joella. Matkalla he kohtaavat sisarukset Marien ja Susannen. Yhteistuumin he paattavat pystyttaa leirin joenrannalle ja viettaa yon juhlien. Aamulla kun he heraavat nuorempi sisko Susanne on kadonnut jaljettomiin. Nayttaa silta, etta Kalix joella on hyvin synkka salaisuus kannettavanaan..

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Ariel kertoo Taistosta (Turo Pajala, Hamlet liikemaailmassa), pohjoissuomalaisesta kaivosmiehesta. Kun kaivos suljetaan, Taisto kaantaa Cadillacin keulan kohti etelaa. Helsingissa Taisto asuu Pelastusarmeijan yomajassa, etsii tyota ja rakastuu uutteraan yksinhuoltajaaitiin. Sitten kohtalo puuttuu peliin. Arielin paaosaa esittava Turo Pajala sai roolistaan Moskovan elokuvajuhlilla parhaan miesnayttelijan palkinnon. Elokuva voitti myos FIPRESCIN palkinnon. Yhdysvalloissa elokuvakriitikot valitsivat Arielin vuoden 1990 parhaaksi ulkomaiseksi elokuvaksi.

programme.title: Odd Man Rush
programme.desc: Odd Man Rush perustuu Bill Keenanin humoristiseen muistelmateokseen, josta tuli jymymenestys. Harvardin latkajoukkueen Bobby Sanders siirtyy pelaamaan Ruotsin alemmille sarjatasoille diilissa, johon liittyy mm. laadukas pesukone. Ruotsissa romanttinen suhde paikalliseen tyttoon pakottaa miehen pohtimaan tarkemmin seka elamaa yleensa etta lapsuuden haavetta NHL:ssa pelaamisesta.

programme.title: Mies vailla menneisyytta
programme.desc: Mies vailla menneisyytta kertoo muistinsa menettavasta miehesta, joka aloittaa elamansa alusta yhteiskunnan koyhimpien keskella. Mies vailla menneisyytta sai Cannesin elokuvajuhlien Grand Prix -palkinnon ja Kati Outinen (Tulitikkutehtaan tytto ja Le Havre) palkittiin roolisuorituksestaan parhaan naisnayttelijan palkinnolla. Elokuvan miespaaosassa nahdaan Markku Peltola (Jadesoturi ja Kauas pilvet karkaavat).

programme.title: Lindell - Yosisko - Osa 2
programme.desc: Brenda Elise Moen ammutaan kuoliaaksi kotinsa ulkopuolella Ullevål Hagebyssa, nahtavasti ilman mitaan motiivia. Cato Isaksen tiimeineen saa jutun tutkittavakseen. Vahitellen poliisi saa selville, etta myos Brenda Elisen lapsenlapsi, 14-vuotias Kathrine Bjerke, on kadonnut. Hanet nahtiin viimeksi kolme kuukautta sitten bussipysakilla Drøbakissa. Rouva Moenilla oli laheinen suhde tyttarentyttareensa. Voiko siina piilla yhteys Kathrinen katoamiseen ja Brenda Elisen surmaan? Hitaasti mutta varmasti varjot vedetaan valoon. Ihmisten pimeat puolet; petokset, epaoikeudenmukaisuus ja salaisuudet ovat aineksia, joka punoutuvat yhteen kauhistuttavaksi tarinaksi.

programme.title: Tulitikkutehtaan tytto
programme.desc: Äitinsa ja isapuolensa kanssa asuva ja tulitikkutehtaan liukuhihnalla tyoskenteleva Iiris (Kati Outinen, Mies vailla menneisyytta ja Le Havre) erehtyy luulemaan tanssiravintolassa kohtaamansa miehen kanssa viettamaansa yota rakkaudeksi. Vaarinkasityksella on kohtalokkaat seuraukset.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-vuotias Anders paattaa matkata Gronlantiin ja ryhtya opettajaksi pienessa kylassa. Hanen vanhempansa ottavat asiaan etaisyytta, silla he olettavat taman ottavan kotitilan haltuunsa, mutta Anders kaipaa maisemanvaihdosta ja uusia haasteita. Elama pienessa kylassa on kovaa – kovempaa kuin Anders oli olettanut. Kylalaiset eivat lampene tulokkaalle, ja mikali han aikoo olla asukkaille – varsinkin lapsille – lainkaan hyodyksi, on hanen tehtava tarkea paatos. Hanen on opittava tuntemaan ihmiset, opeteltava kylan tavoille ja varsinkin tuntea sen perinteet. Vasta sitten aivan uusi maailma aukenee Andersin edessa...

programme.title: Laitakaupungin valot
programme.desc: Laitakaupungin valot kertoo yovartijana tyoskentelevasta Koistisesta, joka joutuu petoksen uhriksi. Laitakaupungin valot oli mukana vuoden 2006 Cannesin elokuvajuhlien kansainvalisessa kilpasarjassa. Elokuva palkittiin parhaan elokuvan Jussi-palkinnolla vuonna 2007. Lisaksi Timo Salminen voitti Jussin parhaasta kuvauksesta ja Markku Patila parhaasta lavastuksesta.

programme.title: 6 Juni
programme.desc: Samira on kaunis 24-vuotias nainen. Hanen perheensa on luvannut hanet vaimoksi miehelle, jota han ei rakasta. Jos Samira ei suostu avioliittoon, hanta uhkaa kunniamurha. Hasse on keski-ikainen mies, joka karsii tuomiota rattijuopumuksesta. Han haaveilee rauhallisesta elamasta vaimonsa ja poikansa kanssa – raittiina. Gertrud on ollut leski jo yhdeksan vuotta. Naapurin Bertil aikoo vihdoinkin voittaa Gertrudin sydamen itselleen ja haudata aviomiehen lopullisesti. Fredrikin tyttoystava on raskaana ja aikoo tehda abortin. 16-vuotias Frederik ei pysty hyvaksymaan tyton paatosta vaan karkaa kotoaan.

programme.title: Hamlet liikemaailmassa
programme.desc: Maailmankirjallisuuden tunnetuin sukudraama on siiretty nykysuomen liike-elaman vallan linnakkeisiin, keskelle Helsingin rock´n rollin tahdissa sykkivaa betoniviidakkoa.

programme.title: Helsinki-Napoli All Night Long
programme.desc: Suomalainen Alex ajaa taksia Berliinin kolkoilla kaduilla. Ilta vaikuttaa alkavan kuten mika tahansa muukin, vaimon heittaminen toihin, Igorin kanssa asioiden hoitelua, mutta sitten kyytiin hyppaa kaksi hamaramiesta suuren rahalaukun kanssa, takaa-ajajat kintereillaan! Pian konnat ovat kuolleita ja Alexilla tehtavanaan ruumiiden havitys..

programme.title: Pida huivista kiinni, Tatjana
programme.desc: Koskenkorvaa litkiva automekaanikko Reino (Matti Pellonpaa) ja kahvista riippuvainen perakamarin poika Valto (Mato Valtonen) lahtevat viettamaan viikonloppua ja kohtaavat matkalla virolaisen Tatjanan (Kati Outinen) ja venalaisen Klavdian (Kirsi Tykkylainen).

programme.title: Lindell - Suruvaippa - Osa 1
programme.desc: Nelja pikkutyttoa valokuvassa. Kaksikymmenta vuotta myohemmin yksi heista loytyy surmattuna. Toinen on kadonnut jaljettomiin. Cato Isaksen on valmiina ratkaisemaan uusia rikosarvoituksia. Menneisyys saavuttaa Lise Sommerin. Paras ystavatar Esther Synnøve Lønn on loytynyt surmattuna ja kurkku auki viillettyna. Joitakin paivia myohemmin myos Estherin poika katoaa. Kun poliisi alkaa rapsuttaa julkisivua, kay ilmi, etta myos eras Lisen ja Esther Synnøven lapsuudenystava on kateissa. Ystavattarien valinen suhde katkee synkkia salaisuuksia. Mita oikeastaan tapahtui tyttojen ollessa pienia?

programme.title: Lindell - Hunajasyotti - Osa 2
programme.desc: On kesa. Elena Bukotaite - jaatelotehtaalla tyoskenteleva liettualaisnainen - ajetaan autolla kuoliaaksi. Samaan aikaan poliisi etsii 8-vuotiasta Høvikissa kadonnutta poikaa. Wiggo Nyman ajaa jaateloautoa alueella. Han oli myos Elenan miesystava. Liittyvatko tapaukset toisiinsa?

programme.title: Bieffekterna
programme.desc: Laaketieteen opiskelijat ja ohjelmoijat Julia ja Rebecca kuuluvat Lundin yliopiston eliittiryhmaan, joka tutkii kiistanalaista tieteellista menetelmaa biohakkerointia, geenitekniikan uutta toivoa, joka saattaa merkita tappavien sairauksien loppua.

programme.title: Blodsbroder
programme.desc: Suoritettuaan pitkan vankilarangaistuksensa Jon on paattanyt aloittaa alusta. Han haluaa opiskella ja elaa ilman huumeita, vakivaltaa ja rikoksia. Lojaalisuus pikkuveljea kohtaan vie hanet kuitenkin pikkuhiljaa takaisin rikollisuuden pariin. Han kohtaa myos suuren rakkautensa Marlenan.

programme.title: Arvottomat
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaen ensimmainen pitka elokuva. Kasikirjoituksen han teki yhdessa veljensa Akin kanssa. Arvottomat on ajaton kuvaus siita kuinka Pikkurikollinen Manne, maalaispoika Harri ja kaunis Veera ajavat Volgalla lapi katoavien suomalaismaisemien, poliisien ja gangsterien roikkuessa herkeamatta kintereilla.. Vauhdikasta matkaa siivittavat mm. Juicen ja Rauli Baddingin ikivihreat kappaleet.

programme.title: Rikos ja rangaistus
programme.desc: Rikos ja rangaistus on moderni tulkinta Dostojevskin kuuluisasta romaanista. Murhaajan (Markku Toikka) ja poliisin (Esko Nikkari, Mies vailla menneisyytta) huimaava psykologinen kaksintaistelu tapahtuu oisen Helsingin sivukujilla ja lain tuolla puolen.

programme.title: Valehtelija
programme.desc: Valehtelija on kuvaus nuoresta huulenheittajasta, joka ei koskaan puhu totta. Aki Kaurismaen esittama nuori mies kuljeskelee pitkin Helsingin katuja ja koittaa lainata rahaa tutuilta ja tuntemattomilta, milloin millakin verukkeella. Valehtelija on Mika Kaurismaen esikoiselokuva seka diplomityo Munchenin elokuvakoulusta.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Siltojen alla asusteleva alkoholisti Matti (Matti Pellonpaa) on saamassa Amerikan tadiltaan huomattavan perinnon, mutta miehen tulisi olla edustuskelpoinen tadin vierailun ajan. Matti kertoo tilanteesta autokauppiaana tyoskentelevalle ystavalleen, joka ehdottaa korvausta vastaan roolien vaihtoa.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg on elamaa suurempi tarina Ruotsin ja Norjan rajalla asuvasta Klemensista (Peter Stomare) ja taman sisarenpojasta, Nejlasta.

programme.title: Ykkoset Ja Nollat - Osa 1
programme.desc: Kriitikoiden ylistama brutaali gangsteridraama Johan Renckilta! FBI ja Interpol saavat vihia suuresta luottokorttisotkusta, ja narkkari Sebbe napataan kiinni epailtyna. Poliisin aloittaessa kuulustelun he saavat kuulla uskomattoman tarinan Goteborgin alamaailmasta. Ruotsalaiset ja venalaiset gangsterit, marokkolaiset hakkerit, korruptoituneet poliitikot ja ahneet virkamiehet - kaikki haluavat ansaita isot rahat, kukaan ei halua olla rakkikoira.

programme.title: Risto
programme.desc: Koko kansan ihailema nayttelija Risto (Risto Kaskilahti) neliraajahalvaantuu tyotapaturmassa. Han saa tapaturman takia mittavan taloudellisen korvauksen seka kansalta valtavan vyoryn sympatiaa. Yhtakkia rahaa on kaikkeen siihen, mita Riston nuori ja kaunis vaimo (Krista Kosonen) on toivonut. Niinpa vaimo luopuu tylsasta tyostaan ja ryhtyy taiteilijaksi. Riston pakkomielteinen, nayttelijaksi pyrkiva pikkuserkku (Aku Hirviniemi) yrittaa hankin hyotya Ristosta kaikin keinoin. Riston parikymppinen poika (Jarkko Niemi) taas hammentaa soppaa rakastumalla aitipuoleensa. Kesken pyorityksen Risto huomaa yllattaen itsessaan toipumisen merkkeja.

programme.title: Zombie ja kummitusjuna
programme.desc: Zombie (Silu Seppala: Leningrad Cowboys) on oman tiensa kulkija, joka ei pysty noudattamaan suomalaisen yhteiskunnan hanelle asettamia normeja. Zombie paattaa jattaa kaiken ja suunnata ulkomaille - paikkaan jossa kukaan ei odota hanelta mitaan. Zombie ja kummitusjuna kuuluu monien mielesta Mika Kaurismaen elokuvien parhaimmistoon. Elokuva palkittiin Parhaan ohjaajan, Parhaan miespaaosan ja Parhaan kuvauksen Jussi-palkinnoilla vuonna 1992. Tragikoominen ja surrealistisenkin Zombien matkassa ovat myos mm. Sleepy Sleepersien Mato Valtonen ja Sakke Jarvenpaa seka tietysti Matti Pellonpaa.

programme.title: Pida huivista kiinni, Tatjana
programme.desc: Koskenkorvaa litkiva automekaanikko Reino (Matti Pellonpaa) ja kahvista riippuvainen perakamarin poika Valto (Mato Valtonen) lahtevat viettamaan viikonloppua ja kohtaavat matkalla virolaisen Tatjanan (Kati Outinen) ja venalaisen Klavdian (Kirsi Tykkylainen).

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Roadmovieta ja rikosdraamaa taidokkaasti yhdisteleva Rosso on kertomus sisilialaisesta palkkamurhaajasta Giancarlo Rossosta, joka on tullut Suomeen etsimaan seuraavaa kohdettaan, joka sattuu olemaan hanen rakastettunsa Marja. Odottamattomasti Rosso saa jaljitysapua Marjan veljelta Martilta, vaikkei heilla ole edes yhteista kielta. Matkalle mahtuu niin romuttamokeikka kuin pari ryostoakin..

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Ariel kertoo Taistosta (Turo Pajala, Hamlet liikemaailmassa), pohjoissuomalaisesta kaivosmiehesta. Kun kaivos suljetaan, Taisto kaantaa Cadillacin keulan kohti etelaa. Helsingissa Taisto asuu Pelastusarmeijan yomajassa, etsii tyota ja rakastuu uutteraan yksinhuoltajaaitiin. Sitten kohtalo puuttuu peliin. Arielin paaosaa esittava Turo Pajala sai roolistaan Moskovan elokuvajuhlilla parhaan miesnayttelijan palkinnon. Elokuva voitti myos FIPRESCIN palkinnon. Yhdysvalloissa elokuvakriitikot valitsivat Arielin vuoden 1990 parhaaksi ulkomaiseksi elokuvaksi.

programme.title: Project Z
programme.desc: Ryhma elokuva-alan opiskelijoita vie kolme tyotonta nayttelijaa lakkautettuun hotelliin Norjan vuoristossa kuvatakseen zombielokuvaa. Fiktio muuttuu faktaksi, kun tuntematon olento alkaa terrorisoida kuvauksia.

programme.title: Ykkoset Ja Nollat - Osa 2
programme.desc: Kriitikoiden ylistama brutaali gangsteridraama Johan Renckilta! FBI ja Interpol saavat vihia suuresta luottokorttisotkusta, ja narkkari Sebbe napataan kiinni epailtyna. Poliisin aloittaessa kuulustelun he saavat kuulla uskomattoman tarinan Goteborgin alamaailmasta. Ruotsalaiset ja venalaiset gangsterit, marokkolaiset hakkerit, korruptoituneet poliitikot ja ahneet virkamiehet - kaikki haluavat ansaita isot rahat, kukaan ei halua olla rakkikoira.

programme.title: Hotet
programme.desc: Lasse Brudell on vastaava ohjelmoija Vidselin lentotukikohdassa Norrbottenissa. Han tyoskentelee huippusalaisen JAS Gripeniin liittyvan EWS-puolustusjarjestelman parissa. Majuri Haglund, karaistunut sotaveteraani, johtaa armeijan erikoisjoukkoja. Miesten tiet kohtaavat, kun Haglund kutsutaan nostamaan turvatoimien tasoa Gripenin ulkomaisille ostajaehdokkaille valmisteltavaa esittelya varten.

programme.title: Bleeder
programme.desc: Louise (Rikke Louise Andersson) rakastaa Leoa (Kim Bodnia) ehdoitta ja on ratketa riemusta kuullessaan odottavansa Leolle lasta. Leo ei ilahdu uutisesta, vaan kokee raskauden tuhoisana esteena tulevaisuudelleen. Paiva paivalta hanen ahdistuksensa kasvaa purkautuen lopulta silmittomana vakivaltana. Louisen veli ei jaa toimettomana katsomaan tilannetta, vaan han paattaa puuttua tapahtumien kulkuun omalla tavallaan. Rakkautta ja anarkiaa -ohjelmistoa

programme.desc: Peter lahestyy kolmeakymmenta, mutta on edelleen eksyksissa ja janoaa rakkautta loputtomien ja tuloksettomien nettideittien avulla. programme.title: No Stranger Than Love
programme.desc: Kaikki kylan miehen ovat rakastuneet Lucyyn. Han on kiltti, sympaattinen, hauska ja lojaali – taydellinen nainen, joka ei tee mitaan vaarin. Mutta nyt han on suostunut romanttiseen tapaamiseen koulun jalkapallojoukkueen naimisissa olevan valmentajan Clintin kanssa. Juuri kun he ovat aloittamassa suhdettaan Clint putoaa aukkoon, joka ilmestyy Lucyn olohuoneen lattiaan. Se ei olekaan mika hyvansa kuoppa, vaan loputon musta aukko, missa Clint kelluu kuin eri ulottuvuudessa.Lucyn taytyy yrittaa pelastaa Clint paljastamatta heidan salaista suhdettaan ja vahemman taydellista puoltaan koko kylalle.

programme.title: Metropolitan
programme.desc: Sosialisti, filosofianortti ja kyyninen keikari – he kaikki ovat osa niin kutsuttua ”urbaania haute bourgeoisieta”, ja vaikka kutakin viehattaa eri ideologia, kaikki ovat yhta vakuuttuneita siita, etta heilla on vastaukset kaikkeen. Ollaan ensimmaisella joululomalla collegesta, ja nuoret aikuiset tapaavat juhlissa ja paivallisilla keskustellakseen loputtomasti. Whit Stillmanin kasikirjoitus sai Oscar-ehdokkuuden, ja hanen debyyttielokuvansa Metropolitan jatti valittomasti jalkensa historiaan seka kulttiklassikkona etta amerikkalaiselokuvien ”pakko nahda” -osaston teoksena.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 SCL 2014 Season 1, Episode 13, Lithunia
programme.desc: The next stage of the competition takes place in Lithunia and world records are once again broken!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S01 : E14 SCL 2014 Season 1, Episode 14, Estonia
programme.desc: Episode 14 takes place in Estonia where drama and world records will be seen again

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S01 : E15 SCL 2014 Season 1, Episode 15, Malaysia (World Finals Part 1)
programme.desc: Taking place over 2 days in Malaysia, this is part 1 of the world finals of Strongman Champions League!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 SCL 2014 Season 1, Episode 16, Malaysia (World Finals Part 2)
programme.desc: Who will be the winner of Strongman Champions League - we find out who is crowned as world champion today in the second part of the final epsiode

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: Across seven rivers, through mountains and forests, 12 strongmen go to toughest places to find out who is strongest Viking in the World and open a new season of Strongman champions league for 2015. Events like the Hercules Hold, Yoke Race and pulling a real Viking ship are some of the ingredients of this fantastic show.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: The second stage of Strongman champions league will be hosted in Germany, by FIBO - the leading international trade show for fitness, wellness and health worldwide with 300,000 visitors in four days. Special implements like the biggest log in the world or the special Bavarian stone lift are not only a challenge, but also an opportunity for new personal, national and world records.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 3, Holland
programme.desc: Holland is hosting 12 different countries with 14 of the strongest men in the world for the third stage of the Strongman Champions League.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 4, Finland
programme.desc: Zydrunas Savickas, one of strongest people on earth is in this competition which has attracted the attention of the audience in the battle for the title of strongest man in Finland. The next round of SCL is in Bulgaria.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 5, Bulgaria
programme.desc: The next stage of the competition is in Bulgaria where Ervin Katona (SCL World Champion 2012) will compete for the last time.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E06 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 6, Latvia
programme.desc: Krzysztof Radzikowski, the leader in the league will fight hard to keep Dainis Zageris off from the title and to gather another 25 ranking points in this next stage in Latvia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 7, Croatia
programme.desc: The competition sees a close battle with a new world record in overhead dumbbell and close finishes throughout the day. This stage is in Croatia, in a city over 1700 years old, steeped in Roman tradition and history, the athletes arrive for the truck pull after a picturesque boat ride on the Adriatic Sea.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 8, Poland
programme.desc: We are now half way through the SCL 2015 and getting closer to the grand world finals in Turkey. The eighth stage is in Poland, the home country of the current leader Krzysztof Radzikowski.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E09 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 9, Austria
programme.desc: In this stage we go into the mountains of Austria to find out through six grueling events who is the strongest in the land of Alps. Martin Wildauer, current World Champion 2014 and Austrian local is competing alongside Zageris, Radzikowski, Belsak and many others.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 10, Romania
programme.desc: The 10th stage of this years competition in Strongman Champions League is held in the Romanian city of Sibiu where the 12 strongmen continue to compete for the title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E11 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 11, World Log Lift Championship
programme.desc: The 11th stage is the SCL Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. In this championship, each competitor must lift three different weights overhead. Zydrunas Savickas is the current world record holder in the Log Lift.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E12 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 12, Lithuania
programme.desc: This next episode of the Strongman Champions League is hosted in Lithuania and sees us getting one step closer to the final.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E13 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 13, Portugal
programme.desc: The 13th stage of Strongman Champions League is in Maia, Portugal. The competition is at the “Powerexpo” – one of the best sport and fitness events in Portugal.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E14 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 14, Martinique
programme.desc: This stage is in Martinique and eight strongmen from all over the world will compete for the last chance to gather points before the world grand finals in December.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E15 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 15, Lightweight World Championship

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E16 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 16, World Finals Turkey
programme.desc: After 15 outstanding competitions all over the world, finally we are here at the final competition of this year’s Strongman Champions League hosted in Turkey.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E01 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 1, Norway - World strongest Viking
programme.desc: Welcome to the land of Vikings - Norway - to the first stage of the SCL World Series 2016

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E02 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: The second stage of the SCL heads to the FIBO convention, Cologne. The leading international trade show for fitness, wellness and health hosts.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E03 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 3, Lithuania - Log lift World championship
programme.desc: For the third stage of SCL world series 2016, the athletes compete in Kaunas for the SCL Log Lift World Championships.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E04 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: Stage four is an epic competition and a few surprises. With 14 strongmen from all over the world, one newcomer left quite an impression.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E05 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 5, Latvia
programme.desc: This year Lauri Nami joins the starting list, back after last years injury in Romania

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E06 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 6, Serbia
programme.desc: The SCL train stopped in Zlatibor for the stage 6 of the MLO SCL. 11 compete for the title in the home country of legendary Ervin Katona.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E07 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 7, Bulgaria
programme.desc: Bulgaria hosts the next stage of the SCL. Current leader in the World Series is Matjaz Belsak, youngest competitor and strongest man of Slovenia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 8, England
programme.desc: The competitors battle it out in the special event, the Atlas Steel Stone. This stone is made completely from iron and cannot be touched with any support.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E09 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 9, Finland
programme.desc: This stage sees the strongmen visit Vaasa, Finland. Residents here are familiar with the competition because some of the SCL icons are from their country.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 10, Finland - World championship under 105 kilograms
programme.desc: 38 athletes compete in the under 90kg and under 105kg SCL World Championships. From each weight class, the top 12 qualify for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E11 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 11, Romania Part 1
programme.desc: A two day, seven event battle with lots of spectators.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E12 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 12, Romania Part 2
programme.desc: Alex Moonen is leading. Part two of the competition in Romania showcases a new challenge - Hercules Hold.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E13 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 13, Curacao
programme.desc: In this stage in Curacao no one wants to lose the chance to fight for one kilo gold in World grand finals in Dubai.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E14 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 14, Portugal
programme.desc: The last chance to qualify for the World Grand Finale. Zageris and Belsak fight for the better position for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E15 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 15, Dubai World grand finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E16 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 16, Dubai World grand finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this last episode, the best athletes compete in Pole Push, Deadlift, Forward Hold and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: We are in beautiful Norway for the kick off of the 2017 MLO Strongman Champions League season. With partly cloudy weather and lots of snow, we have the perfect scenery for the athletes, who prepare for the first contest of the year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: A definite highlight in this FIBO edition in Germany, Strongman Champions League introduced its new rules for a special team item. Graham Hicks tries here to set a New World Record on the biggest log in the world, currently held by Krzysztof Radzikowski. Boosted also by the presence of the acclaimed in the strongman circles names of Mark Felix and Danis Zageris.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 3, Lithuania
programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 5, Serbia
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 6, Canada (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E07 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 7, Canada (Part 2)
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E08 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E09 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E10 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.
